title:
90’s baby 💎

I spent most of November away from social media. In an age where we are all instantly accessible at the cl...
description: 90â€™s baby ðŸ’Ž I spent most of November away from social media. In an age where we are all instantly accessible at the click of a button, there is something almost deliciously luxurious about disconnecting from the online world and the happenings beyond your peripheral vision, just for a little while. Just being fully present and connected to the life that you can tangibly touch with your fingertips, the world you can interact with and experience with your own flesh. To a certain extent it brings me back to being a kid, where my whole world simply was my family, friends, home, and immediate surroundings, and seeing the outside world meant actually traveling somewhere to experience it rather than observing through the lens of someone elseâ€™s photos on instagram. There was something so precious about that unadulterated experience of pure connectedness to yourself and those around you. Pre-smartphone, sitting in silence for a while and just observing what was around us was our default setting - now we have to actively seek out and intentionally commit to quietening out the external noise in order to listen to what is truly going on in our heart and minds. For some people perhaps that is daunting, others may fear boredom, but it can also be immensely peaceful, grounding and make you truly grateful for what you have and can create in your own beautiful life. . . . . . #ukmodel #ukmodels #londonmodels #londonmodel #portsinspired #portsvision #portraitsvision #portraitsshotz #portraiturephotography #portraitinspiration #fashionmodelshoot #studioportrait #studioportraits #portraits_perfection #theportraitculture #theportraitcentral #ukmodelsearch #portraitsmood #ukportraits #londonportraits #portraitspage #portraitmodel #beautymodel #fashionportrait #studiophotoshoot #portraitspage #wickedports #portraitsinspire #eurasianmodel #commercialmodels #90soutfit
